      <description><![CDATA[<b>Rise and Fall of a Temple</b><br><i>Arts &amp; Culture</i><br>Fri 6th Feb – Fri 17th Jul<br>Chelsea Space, Pimlico<br>Free<br><br>Major exhibition by artist Eva Sajovic featuring multimedia artworks including sculptures, knitted tapestries, embroidery, ceramics and film inspired by Ancient Rome, exploring concepts of empire, power and legacy.<br><br><a href="https://secretldn.com/things-to-do-in-london-weekend/">More info / tickets</a>]]></description>
